sec.p:
The secondary objectives are to:
assess whether the Embedding Package increases referral to and uptake of structured education, as well as improving biomedical and psychosocial outcomes;
assess sustainability of the Embedding Package using an observational follow-up period;
contextualise the process of implementation, sustainability of the change and the ‘fit’ of the Embedding Package within routine practice;
assess cost-effectiveness of the Embedding Package.
